'''查尔斯·伍德森'''（{{lang-en|Charles Woodson}}，{{bd|1976年|10月7日}}），退役[[美式足球|美式足球]][[角卫|角卫]]，曾先後效力於[[國家美式足球聯盟|國家美式足球聯盟]]的[[绿湾包装工|绿湾包装工]]和[[奥克兰突袭者|奥克兰突袭者]]。此外，伍德森還是至今唯一一位贏得[[海斯曼獎|海斯曼獎]]的防守球員<ref>{{cite web
 | url =https://www.espn.com/college-football/story/_/id/21677799/peyton-manning-charles-woodson-randy-moss-1997-heisman-trophy
 | title =The oral history of the epic 1997 Heisman Trophy race
 | author =Chris Low
 | date =2017-12-06
 | website =ESPN.com
 | publisher =[[ESPN|ESPN]]
 | access-date =
 | quote =When Woodson edged Manning to become the first primarily defensive player to win the coveted award, it set off howls of protests in Knoxville, Tennessee. To this day, fans on all sides fiercely debate if the voters got it right.
